NAKKADY
</taxonomicName>
, p. 691, pl. 90, figs. 29-32.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFF7FFB6FC959DB96D057F51" blockId="26.[831,1437,451,561]" pageId="26" pageNumber="40">
1953. 
<taxonomicName id="8DDC4D70FFF7FFB6FC289DB96DD67F72" authority="NAKKADY." authorityName="NAKKADY." box="[898,1243,509,531]" class="Globothalamea" family="Anomalinidae" genus="Anomalina" kingdom="Chromista" order="Rotaliida" pageId="26" pageNumber="40" phylum="Foraminifera" rank="species" species="pseudoacuta">
